The '''Arkanian Renegades''' were a group of geneticists on [[Arkania/Legends|Arkania]] who attempted to overthrow the [[Arkanian Dominion|planet's government]] in [[50 BBY/Legends|50 BBY]]. They objected to the systematic alteration of the [[Yaka]] [[Species/Legends|species]] by means of involuntary [[Cybernetics/Legends|cybernetic]] implants, and built a legendary army of [[Assimilator]] [[Cyborg/Legends|cyborgs]] almost from scratch to defeat the Dominion. They were ultimately defeated by the timely intervention of the [[Jedi Knight/Legends|Jedi Knights]], but some of their creations&mdash;[[Gorm (cyborg)|Gorm the Dissolver]] among them&mdash;lived on.

